Interface ModuleMetricEntityInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:

public interface ModuleMetricEntityInterface
Every venice Module that defines its set of MetricEntity should implement this interface.

    • getUniqueMetricEntities

      static Collection<MetricEntity> getUniqueMetricEntities(Class<? extends ModuleMetricEntityInterface>... enumClasses)
      Get all the unique MetricEntity from the provided enum classes based on the metric name. This will also check if there are multiple metric entities with the same name across the provided enum classes with different metric types and throw.
